title: Casket (disambiguation)

properties.name: description
properties.value: Casket may refer to the following:

content:
Casket may refer to the following:

  • Casket, a low-value, tradeable item generally obtained from fishing or as a monster drop
  • Casket (Pirate's Treasure), the reward of the quest Pirate's Treasure.
  • Casket (Reward pool), possible reward from the reward pool after defeating Tempoross.
  • Treasure Trails caskets, a casket containing the next clue step or the reward for the respective trail:
    • Reward casket (beginner) - from beginner clue scrolls
    • Reward casket (easy) - from easy clue scrolls
    • Reward casket (medium) - from medium clue scrolls
    • Reward casket (hard) - from hard clue scrolls
    • Reward casket (elite) - from elite clue scrolls
    • Reward casket (master) - from master clue scrolls
    • Heavy casket - from completing 200 elite Treasure Trails
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
